\b\fs24 Project Information\b0\fs22\par
\par
\b PDF Merger\b0  is a Windows desktop application for merging PDF files with specialized support for single-side ADF (Automatic Document Feeder) scanners.\par
\par
\b Features:\b0\par
{\pntext\f1\'B7\tab}Sequential Merge - Combine multiple PDF files into one\par
{\pntext\f1\'B7\tab}ADF Odd/Even Merge - Interleave pages from single-side scanners\par
{\pntext\f1\'B7\tab}Thesis Update - Insert signature and declaration pages\par
\par
\b Website:\b0  https://ucoruh.github.io/pdf-merger/\par
\b Source Code:\b0  https://github.com/ucoruh/pdf-merger\par
\b Author:\b0  Asst. Prof. Dr. Ugur CORUH\par
